dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.axis

Interface ISwAxisIndividual

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, ISwCalprmAxisTypeProps

    public interface ISwAxisIndividual
extends IEntity, ISwCalprmAxisTypeProps
    ISwAxisIndividual: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This meta-class describes an axis integrated into a parameter (field etc.). The integration makes this individual to each parameter. The so-called grouped axis represents the counterpart to this. It is conceived as an independent parameter (see class SwAxisGrouped).

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
